OL,3,CCornish charity providing emergency
OL,4,Caid following devastating flooding
OL,6,FA Cornish charity has been providing
OL,7,Femergency shelter in Malawi after
OL,8,Fsevere flooding in East Africa.
OL,10,FShelterBox is warning more than 12,000
OL,11,Fpeople have been displaced, with many
OL,12,Fhomes still submerged by floodwater.
OL,14,FThe flooding has also damaged
OL,15,Finfrastructure including roads and
OL,16,Fbridges, and many crops have been
OL,17,Fdestroyed, making it harder for people
OL,18,Fto access food, water and shelter, the
OL,19,Fcharity said.
