OL,3,CCornish charity providing emergency
OL,4,Caid following devastating flooding
OL,6,FIt comes after a period of heavy
OL,7,Frainfall over the past month.
OL,9,FShelterBox said a response team from
OL,10,Fthe charity has been working with
OL,11,Flocals to distribute tarpaulins,
OL,12,Ftools, water filters, solar lights,
OL,13,Fand other essential items.
OL,15,FThe team has also been working with
OL,16,Flocal organisations to show people how
OL,17,Fthey can use the tools and tarpaulins
OL,18,Fto protect their homes, the charity
OL,19,Fadded.
