OL,6,FMr Strutton added the charity is also
OL,7,Fworking with government agencies, the
OL,8,FMalawian Red Cross Society and Rotary
OL,9,Fto find ways to mitigate the impact of
OL,10,Ffuture floods.
OL,12,FHe said: "Floods, storms and droughts
OL,13,Fare getting worse, hitting the same
OL,14,Fplaces more often and lasting longer.
OL,15,FPeople often don't have time to
OL,16,Frecover from an emergency before the
OL,17,Fnext takes its toll.
